<item>
            <title>[LU-7533] remove obsolete idmap functionality</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-7533</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;With the landing of the nodemap functionality, the old remote client idmap functionality should be removed from the Lustre code.  This includes &lt;tt&gt;lustre/include/lustre_idmap.c&lt;/tt&gt;, &lt;tt&gt;lustre/obdclass/idmap.c&lt;/tt&gt;, and &lt;tt&gt;lustre/mdt/mdt_idmap.c&lt;/tt&gt; and their callsites.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Also, the Lustre user manual should be updated to remove the associated functionality.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
